Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:57.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Into the sky of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:04.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}You put all your strength and fighting spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Can you do it? I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:13.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Your heart is always geared up\Nfor a critical battle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:17.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}You're world-famous brave men
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:23.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Even if life's easy here, you call it Cro, Cro
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:37.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(350,500)}Ah, Cromartie is our alma mater
