Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When you have many things you have to do\Nand you might forget what they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,you should write each of them down\Non paper and put it on your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please... Say something...
